### 感谢您的回复

#### 对于您的回复 我的一些朴素的思考

- 为什么是$z = \gamma n + \beta$ 的形式，如果使用一个全连接层呢？ 在收到您的邮件后我产生了这样的疑惑。在学习了斯坦福的一个课程CS231n“批量归一化”之后，其中一个说法给了我很大的启发: $\gamma ,\beta $ 的极限情况是 $ \gamma = \sqrt{\sigma_B^2 + \epsilon }， \beta = \mu_B $ ，然而在 $\gamma $在 等于 1 和 等于$\sqrt{\sigma_B^2 + \epsilon} $之间学习，就赋予了网络很大的灵活性，最终训练为一个对所有batch都合适的$\gamma$。（我之前错误理解为每个维度全部移动到0处，这看起来仿佛必然丧失掉数据的信息，怎么还会加快网络的收敛呢）
- 但这样或许这就和正态分布化，没有很大的关联。（？）因为我认为一个batch只有32或者64个样本的归一化，只有归一化到合适区间的效果，达不到高斯分布的大量样本的要求。不知道我的现在的理解是否正确。

#### 第二个问题

- 接上文，这就给我带来的第二个疑问，输入的数据是什么分布。我认为对于给数字的十分类，数据可以根据标签分成10份，每一份的全部数据成高斯分布，而不同份的数据之间应该没有关系。我不理解为何一开始的时候，可以对所有数据一起进行归一化处理？

#### 在推导公式的时候遇到一些问题，还烦请您看一下

##### BN层，假设X只有一个特征

$$输入\left[ \begin{matrix} 
x_1\\ x_2 \\x_3  \end{matrix} \right] \rightarrow 
归一\left[ \begin{matrix} 
n_1\\ n_2 \\n_3  \end{matrix} \right] \rightarrow
伸缩 (\gamma ) +移动(\beta)各个特征维度\left[ \begin{matrix} 
z_1\\ z_2 \\z_3  \end{matrix} \right]\leftarrow
下一层的回传\left[ \begin{matrix} 
\delta_1\\ \delta_2 \\\delta_3  \end{matrix} \right] 
$$

##### 对于前传误差公式13，**我进行了如下的推导** (符号定义沿用教程) 

$$
n_i = f_n(x_i,\mu_B,\sigma_B^2) =  {x_i-\mu_B \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}} \tag{8}
$$

$$
\mu_B =   {1 \over m}\sum_1^m x_i \tag{6}
$$

$$
\sigma^2_B = f_\sigma(x_1,...,x_m, \mu_B) = {1 \over m} \sum_1^m (x_i-\mu_B)^2 \tag{7}
$$

$$
\begin{aligned}
{\partial J \over \partial x_k} 
&= \sum_{i=1}^m {\partial J \over \partial z_i}{\partial z_i \over \partial x_k} 
\\
&= \sum_{i=1}^m \delta_i \cdot {\partial z_i \over \partial x_k}
\\
&= \sum_{i=1}^m \delta_i \cdot {d z_i \over d n_i}{\partial n_i \over \partial x_k} 
\\
&= \sum_{i=1}^m \delta_i \cdot \gamma \cdot {\partial n_i \over \partial x_k} 
\\
&= \gamma · \sum_{i=1}^m \delta_i \cdot ({\partial f_n\over \partial x_k} + {\partial f_n \over \partial  \sigma^2_B}{\partial  \sigma^2_B \over \partial x_k} + {\partial f_n \over \partial  \mu_B}{\partial  \mu_B \over \partial x_k} )
\\
&= \gamma · \sum_{i=1}^m \delta_i \cdot ({\partial f_n \over \partial x_k} 
+{\partial f_n \over \partial  \sigma^2_B }{\partial \sigma^2_B \over \partial x_k} 
+{\partial f_n \over \partial  \mu_B}{\partial  \mu_B \over \partial x_k} )
\\
&= \gamma · \sum_{i=1}^m \delta_i \cdot \{ {\partial f_n \over \partial x_k} 
+{\partial f_n \over \partial \sigma^2_B }[{\partial f_{\sigma} \over \partial x_k}+{\partial f_{\sigma} \over \partial \mu_B}{\partial \mu_B \over \partial x_k} ]
+{\partial f_n \over \partial  \mu_B}{\partial  \mu_B \over \partial x_k} \}
\\
&= \gamma · \sum_{i=1}^m \delta_i \{ {\partial f_n \over \partial x_k} 
\\
&+( x_k-\mu_B)  (-{1 \over 2}(\sigma^2_B + \epsilon)^{-3/2})[{2(x_k - \mu_B) \over m} -{2 \over m} \sum _{i=1}^m(x_i-\mu_B)\cdot {1 \over m}]
\\
&+{-1 \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}}\cdot{1 \over m} \} 
\\
&其中 i = k 时：{\partial f_n \over \partial x_k} ={1 \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}} \qquad i!=k时：{\partial f_n \over \partial x_k} = 0
\end{aligned} \tag{13'} 
$$

代入X = $[x_1,x_2,x_3]$,m = 3

$$
\begin{aligned}
{dJ \over dx_1} 
&= \gamma · \sum_{i=1}^m \delta_i \{ {\partial f_n \over \partial x_1} 
+( x_k-\mu_B)  (-{1 \over 2}(\sigma^2_B + \epsilon)^{-3/2})[{2(x_1 - \mu_B) \over m} -{2 \over m} \sum _{i=1}^m(x_i-\mu_B)\cdot {1 \over m}]
+{-1 \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}}\cdot{1 \over m} \} 
\\
&= \gamma ·  \sum_{i=1}^m \delta_i \{ {\partial f_n \over \partial x_1} 
+( x_1-\mu_B)  (-{1 \over 2}(\sigma^2_B + \epsilon)^{-3/2}){2(x_1 - \mu_B) \over m} 
+{-1 \over m\sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}} \} 
\\
&= \gamma · \{{ \delta_1  \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon} } +(\delta_1 + \delta_2 + \delta_3)[
( x_1-\mu_B)^2  (-(\sigma^2_B + \epsilon)^{-3/2}){1\over m} 
+{-1 \over m\sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}} ]\} 
\\
&= \gamma  \{ {\delta_1 \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}} -  { (x_1 - \mu_B)^2 + \sigma_B^2 +\epsilon  \over m\sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}} (\delta_1 + \delta_2 + \delta_3)\}
\\
&其中 {\partial f_n \over \partial x_1} ={1 \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}} ,\quad {\partial f_n \over \partial x_2} =  {\partial f_n \over \partial x_3} = 0
\end{aligned} 
$$

##### 教程中式(13)代入X = $[x_1,x_2,x_3]$,m = 3

**（另外式子中$\delta \cdot \gamma $应该是矩阵？它是如何参与运算的?）**
$$
\begin{aligned}
{dJ \over dx_1} 
&= {\delta \cdot \gamma \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}} + {dJ \over d\sigma^2_B} \cdot {2(x_1 - \mu_B) \over m} + {dJ \over d\mu_B} \cdot {1 \over m}
\\
&= {\delta \cdot \gamma \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}} + {dJ \over d\sigma^2_B} \cdot {2(x_1 - \mu_B) \over m} +( {dJ \over d n_i}{d n_i \over d \mu_B} + {dJ \over  d\sigma^2_B}{d \sigma^2_B \over d \mu_B})\cdot {1 \over m}
\\
&= {\delta \cdot \gamma \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}} + {dJ \over d\sigma^2_B} \cdot {2(x_1 - \mu_B) \over m} +( {dJ \over d n_i}{d n_i \over d \mu_B} + {dJ \over  d\sigma^2_B}{d \sigma^2_B \over d \mu_B})\cdot {1 \over m}
\\
&= {\delta \cdot \gamma \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}} + {dJ \over d\sigma^2_B} \cdot {2(x_1 - \mu_B) \over m} + {dJ \over d n_i}{d n_i \over d \mu_B} \cdot {1 \over m}
\\
&= {\delta \cdot \gamma \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}} 
\\
&+ (-{1 \over 2}(\sigma^2_B + \epsilon)^{-3/2}\sum_{i=1}^m {dJ \over d n_i}  (x_i-\mu_B) )\cdot{2(x_1-\mu_B) \over m}
\\
&+ (-{\delta \cdot \gamma \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}}) \cdot {1 \over m}
\\
&= (1- {1 \over m}){\delta \cdot \gamma \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}}+ (-{1 \over 2}(\sigma^2_B + \epsilon)^{-3/2}\sum_{i=1}^m {dJ \over d n_i}  (x_i-\mu_B) )\cdot{2(x_1-\mu_B) \over m}
\\
&= (1- {1 \over m}){\delta \cdot \gamma \over \sqrt{\sigma^2_B + \epsilon}}-(\sigma^2_B + \epsilon)^{-3/2} {(x_1-\mu_B) \over m} \{ (\delta_1 x_1 +\delta_2 x_2 + \delta_3 x_3)-(\delta_1 + \delta_2 + \delta_3)\mu_B)\}
\end{aligned}
$$

